OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773765951
OL,3,CMan's body found inside car four
OL,4,Cmonths after disappearing into River
OL,5,CTrent
OL,7,FA man's body has been found inside a
OL,8,Fcar four months after it went missing
OL,9,Fin the River Trent in Nottingham.
OL,11,FThe vehicle was located in Nottingham
OL,12,Fbetween Sandringham Avenue and County
OL,13,FHall at around 3.30pm on Sunday 15
OL,14,FMarch, after months of police searches.
OL,16,FPolice have confirmed the car is the
OL,17,Fsame vehicle which entered the river
OL,18,Fnear to the Wilford Suspension Bridge
OL,19,Fon 15 November 2025.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
