PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773765951
OL,3,CMan's body found inside car four
OL,4,Cmonths after disappearing into River
OL,5,CTrent
OL,7,FA man's body, believed to be the
OL,8,Fregistered keeper of the car, was
OL,9,Ffound inside the car today and has
OL,10,Fbeen recovered from the river by
OL,11,Fpolice divers.
OL,13,FSearches of the river have been taking
OL,14,Fplace since November with the support
OL,15,Fof Humberside Police and a specialist
OL,16,FHome Office unit.
OL,18,FThe missing vehicle was identified on
OL,19,FSunday after an additional search by a
OL,20,Fspecialist charity.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773765951
OL,3,CMan's body found inside car four
OL,4,Cmonths after disappearing into River
OL,5,CTrent
OL,7,FDetective Sergeant Millie Gillett, of
OL,8,FNottinghamshire Police, said:
OL,10,F"Our thoughts are with this man's
OL,11,Ffamily and they have been updated and
OL,12,Foffered support.
OL,14,F"While our investigation into what
OL,15,Fhappened continues, we don't believe
OL,16,Fhis death to be suspicious and a file
OL,17,Fwill be prepared for the coroner.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
