OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773765951
OL,3,CMan's body found inside car four
OL,4,Cmonths after disappearing into River
OL,5,CTrent
OL,7,F"Underwater search teams have worked
OL,8,Fhard in their efforts to locate the
OL,9,Fcar and any possible occupants since
OL,10,Fthe investigation was launched.
OL,12,F"However, these efforts have been
OL,13,Fhampered by high river levels and
OL,14,Fheavy rainfall.
OL,16,F"Detectives have also been working to
OL,17,Festablish what exactly led to the
OL,18,Fvehicle going into the water.
OL,20,F"I would continue to ask that people
OL,21,Fdo not speculate on what has happened."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU|D@AOU}D@gO]
